data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This 1-year-old, meticulously designed and well-maintained 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence is a true gem, nestled on a spacious 0.5-acre lot. The kitchen features granite countertops and a large island. The open-concept layout seamlessly connects the living room, breakfast area, and kitchen, creating the perfect environment for both entertaining and everyday living. The main level also features a separate dining room, a great room with a fireplace, laundry room, and powder room. The upper level features a master bedroom that has a private bath with double vanities and large walk-in closet, as well as 3 additional bedrooms and a full bath. This home boasts a full unfinished basement with endless possibilities, allowing you to tailor the space to fit your unique lifestyle. Conveniently located in a desirable neighborhood, this property offers a perfect balance of serenity and accessibility. You'll find yourself within close proximity to schools, parks, shopping, and dining options, making it a truly coveted location.
